    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the saffron infuses, add your <strong>couscous</strong> to a large bowl with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and your <strong>chopped dates</strong>, then cover and set aside</p><p>Add your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> to the <strong>infused saffron water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix to combine – this is your <strong>saffron yoghurt</strong></p>",
