      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>free range chicken breasts portions</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>",
