      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped chicken</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 7-8 min until browned</p><p>Add your <strong>sumac</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
